{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}Any more objections?{\r}

632
01:13:05,066 --> 01:13:08,194
{\fs14}剩下的人去总督码头，快走！{\r}
{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}The rest of you proceed to the Governor's dock. Get moving!{\r}

633
