{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}First you'll watch your people go one by one.{\r}

649
01:17:42,889 --> 01:17:44,725
{\fs14}总有一天我会杀了你{\r}
{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}Someday I'll kill you.{\r}

650
01:17:46,351 --> 01:17:47,561
{\fs14}军官！{\r}
{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}Officer!{\r}

651
01:17:53,817 --> 01:17:55,861
