01:19:11,479 --> 01:19:12,689
{\fs14}格鲁达{\r}
{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}Gruda.{\r}

671
01:19:14,399 --> 01:19:16,943
{\fs14}格鲁达，总有一天我要杀了你{\r}
{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}Gruda, someday I'll kill you.{\r}

