690
01:21:01,090 --> 01:21:03,718
{\fs14}他们没有机会战胜格鲁达的精锐部队{\r}
{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}They don't have a chance against Gruda's crack troops.{\r}

691
01:21:03,801 --> 01:21:06,888
