696
01:21:25,281 --> 01:21:27,033
{\fs14}谁能肯定我们不能...{\r}
{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}Who knows what we may accomplish...{\r}

697
01:21:27,117 --> 01:21:30,245
{\fs14}战胜落后的格鲁达男爵和他落后的世界？{\r}
{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}against the outdated Baron Gruda and his outdated world?{\r}

698
01:21:30,328 --> 01:21:32,622
