01:22:27,845 --> 01:22:30,347
{\fs14}“科学证明，没有什么是不可能的”{\r}
{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&\b0\i1}"Science has learned that nothing is impossible. "{\r}

710
01:22:33,726 --> 01:22:35,978
